<office:document-content filename="erp5_list.sxc" xmlns:draw='http://openoffice.org/2000/drawing' xmlns:office='http://openoffice.org/2000/office'
 xmlns:text='http://openoffice.org/2000/text' xmlns:number='http://openoffice.org/2000/datastyle'
 xmlns:chart='http://openoffice.org/2000/chart' xmlns:table='http://openoffice.org/2000/table'
 xmlns:dr3d='http://openoffice.org/2000/dr3d' xmlns:fo='http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Format'
 xmlns:style='http://openoffice.org/2000/style' xmlns:form='http://openoffice.org/2000/form'
 xmlns:script='http://openoffice.org/2000/script' xmlns:svg='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' 
 xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink' xmlns:math='http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML' 
 xmlns:meta='http://openoffice.org/2000/meta'
 xmlns:dc='http://purl.oclc.org/dc'
 office:class='spreadsheet' xmlns:tal='http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal'
 xmlns:i18n='http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n'
 xmlns:metal='http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal'
 tal:attributes='dummy python:request.RESPONSE.setHeader("Content-Type", "text/html;; charset=utf-8")'
 office:version='1.0'>
 
 <!--Definition of Styles--> 
 <office:automatic-styles>
 <tal:block metal:define-macro="listbox">
 <tal:block tal:repeat='column_title python: column_width'>
 <tal:block tal:condition="python: str(column_title)!='section_name'">
 <tal:block tal:define="width python: column_width[column_title]; marie python:here.log('hhh',column_title)"> 
 <style:style style:family='table-column' style:name='TableColumn' tal:attributes='style:name python: column_title'>
 <style:properties style:column-width='4.168cm' 
 tal:attributes="style:column-width python:str(width)+str('cm')" fo:break-before='auto'/>
 </style:style>
 </tal:block>
 </tal:block>
 </tal:block>
 
 <style:style style:family='table-row' style:name='TableRowTitle'>
 <style:properties style:use-optimal-row-height='false' style:row-height='0.45cm' fo:break-before='auto'/>
 </style:style>
 <style:style style:family='table-row' style:name='TableRowContents'>
 <style:properties style:use-optimal-row-height='false' style:row-height='0.45cm' fo:break-before='auto'/>
 </style:style>
 <style:style style:master-page-name='Default' style:family='table' style:name='Table'>
 <style:properties table:display='true' fo:border='0.002cm solid #000000'/>
 </style:style>
 <style:style style:parent-style-name='Default' style:family='table-cell' style:name='TableCellTitle'>
 <style:properties fo:font-weight='bold' fo:color='#4c4c4c' fo:font-size='9pt' fo:border='0.002cm solid #000000' style:text-align-source='fix' fo:margin-left='0cm' fo:font-style='italic' fo:background-color='#cccccc' fo:vertical-align='middle' fo:text-align='start' />
 </style:style>
 <style:style style:parent-style-name='Default' style:family='table-cell' style:name='TableCellContents'>
 <style:properties fo:margin-left='0cm' fo:vertical-align='bottom' fo:border='0.002cm solid #000000' style:text-align-source='fix' fo:text-align='start' fo:wrap-option='no-wrap'/>
 </style:style>
 <style:style style:parent-style-name='Default' style:family='table-cell' style:name='TableCellSection1'>
 <style:properties fo:border-bottom='0.002cm solid #000000' style:text-align-source='value-type' fo:border-right='none' fo:border-left='none' fo:border-top='0.002cm solid #000000' fo:margin-left='0cm'/>
 </style:style>
 <style:style style:parent-style-name='Default' style:family='table-cell' style:name='TableCellSection3'>
 <style:properties fo:border-bottom='0.002cm solid #000000' style:text-align-source='value-type' fo:border-right='none' fo:border-left='0.002cm solid #000000' fo:border-top='0.002cm solid #000000' fo:margin-left='0cm'/>
 </style:style>
 
 <style:style style:parent-style-name='Default' style:family='table-cell' style:name='TableCellSection5'>
 <style:properties style:text-align-source='value-type' fo:border-bottom='0.002cm solid #000000' fo:border-left='0.002cm solid #000000' fo:border-right='0.002cm solid #000000' fo:margin-left='0cm'/>
 </style:style>
 <style:style style:parent-style-name='Default' style:family='table-cell' style:name='TableCellSection2'>
 <style:properties style:text-align-source='value-type' fo:border-='none' fo:margin-left='0cm'/>
 </style:style>
 <style:style style:parent-style-name='Default' style:family='table-cell' style:name='TableCellSection4'>
 <style:properties style:text-align-source='value-type' fo:border-left='0.002cm solid #000000' fo:border-right='0.002cm solid #000000' fo:margin-left='0cm'/>
 </style:style>
 
 </tal:block>
 </office:automatic-styles>
 
 
 </office:document-content>
